Memo to haters. Twitter is like being on a conveyer belt, there will be a never ending supply of idiots and jerks that come and go on Twitter threads. Whether you stop the belt to dance with any one of them is up to you. While I love respectful debate,

I am not a fan of vitriol. So I will actively block, especially those that are in the cheap seats shrouded by anonymity. It has been my experience that one negative voice aimed at me has the incredible power to drown out ten positive ones. One of the best things I can achieve

is to never let it. I have come to realize that the most obnoxious, obsessed and hateful on Twitter are the least verbal in real life and I can assure you that most social media trolls have no physical troll land to dwell. So hate and go and alienate (as Larry David would say,

I could give a fuck) piped.video/watch?v=txzdEKmw… So, debate here pleasantly and respectfully or be blocked and banished post haste - joining your Twitter troll brethren in the ether of the Twittersphere, never to be heard of again. To lovers, haters and those that dont give a damn
Be safe.
